omizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMultiPolyline","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":" instances. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNPointCollection","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/addAnnotation:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adds an annotation to the map view."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/addAnnotation:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/addannotation:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"addAnnotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":" instances, and the line segments that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path along which something moves.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNPolyline","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"}}}